title: Elfquest Graphic Novel 8: Kings of the Broken Wheel
description: Rayek has kidnapped Cutter and his tribe, leaving them in the past. Thousands of years later, Rayek will attempt to correct the mistake that first brought the elves to this world. If he succeeds, the Wolfriders will never have existed But the only ones who could possibly stop him are long gone...
author: Wendy Pini
